title: IAA Tonight | Would Ja Morant Have 'Cooked' Michael Jordan?
description: Ja Morant had some spicy comments in a recent interview he did with Bleacher Report's Taylor Rooks, stating that he would've 'cooked' Michael Jordan. Antoine Walker, Omar Kelly, and Auntie Chantel Tremitiere discuss whether Ja should have that level of confidence or if he needs to humble himself.
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Antoine Walker, Omar Kelly, Chantel Tremitiere)
